{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it made me-- now, I'm getting older, I'm getting 14, 15-- it made me very angry, that I didn't think he was honest about these things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, you know, I was imbued with honesty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you a little later about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I felt, for instance, that why that it was so important that everything was, you know, exactly done the right way when he knew that his wife wasn't doing it always?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did he have to be so rigid about these things?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I have to say, in terms of religion, I have was very religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was also-- I'm getting to be 12 and 14 years old-- very interested in art.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to these wonderful Berlin museums and I saw all Christian art too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't say that it was anything wrong or that it was that religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my Jewish colleagues in school thought I was terrible that I knew, meanwhile, who the apostles were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't become Christian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just thought it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is a period-- aged 12, 13-- that I could talk probably for the rest of the time, which I will not do, that had enormous impact on my life.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was art, it was reading, it were the revolutionary writers in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was impact my father too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I was eight years old, he took me into the Tiergarten and said, here are people who have killed Rosa Luxemburg-- L-U-X-E-M-B-U-R-G-- and Libknecht-- L-I-B-K-N-E-C-H-T.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who were revolutionaries.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, they killed them here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, my father said, I didn't agree with them because they were for violence, and he was not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a pacifist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But still, one doesn't kill people for their opinion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, this is much earlier.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
